    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been absolutely wonderful to me. It\u2019s in great shape and runs like a dream\u2014perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways! It\u2019s been well-loved and well-maintained, so it\u2019s totally ready for its next adventure. There are a few tiny signs of life here and there, but honestly, it still looks sharp and feels solid on the road. Drop me a message if you want to come by for a test drive or have any questions!",
