    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This naturally aspirated mill utilizes individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system to produce a high-revving power band reaching an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels via a variable M-differential lock. The chassis remains composed, having undergone rear subframe reinforcement to mitigate common floor pan fatigue, while the suspension retains its factory-spec geometry for precise turn-in. Maintenance is up to date, including a recent valve shim adjustment and cooling system refresh. While the aesthetics reflect its status as a well-loved driver\u2019s car, the mechanical synchronization and drivetrain rigidity are excellent.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
