    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that's been super well-loved? This beauty is in great shape and totally ready for its next big adventure with you! It runs like an absolute dream and has plenty of life left in it for weekend getaways or just zipping around town. It's clean, comfy, and honestly just a joy to drive. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself\u2014you're going to love it!",
